        "subject": "LU-3472 ldlm: MDS can't umount with blocked flock",
        "message": "LU-3472 ldlm: MDS can't umount with blocked flock\n\nAdd ldlm_flock_blocking_unlink() to\nldlm_resource_unlink_lock().\nIt is needed to be called during server side\ncleanup_resource()\n\nXyratex-bug-id: MRP-997\nSigned-off-by: Andriy Skulysh <Andriy_Skulysh@xyratex.com>\nReviewed-by: Alexander Boyko <Alexander_Boyko@xyratex.com>\nReviewed-by: Vitaly Fertman <Vitaly_Fertman@xyratex.com>\nChange-Id: I49c9b1b5ada898ddd20c134b448beed9b44c5b3a\n"
